The paper deals with optimization of power allocation in a communication system with caching and non-orthogonal multiple access (NOMA), which are both relevant to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses fairness among users, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). The proposed deep reinforcement learning method falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
